SUMMARY:Are Your Ducks in a Row?
DESCRIPTION:Advance Care Planning Workshop\nNone of us want to think about it\, right? But at some point in the future\, we all may face a situation where important decisions must be made\nabout our healthcare\, but we are unable to speak for ourselves. Or perhaps this has happened to a loved one. Are you prepared? \nCome to this workshop at the Garner Senior Center to learn how to get your ducks in a row. This will be an informative workshop about advanced care planning\, healthcare\, proxies\, legal paperwork\, and will include an interactive exercise that will clarify your thoughts.
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/are-your-ducks-in-a-row-2/
LOCATION:Garner Senior Centr\, 205 E. Garner Road\, Garner\, 27529\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community Events
