SUMMARY:Expressive Arts (virtual)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for this ongoing virtual expressive arts group. Facilitators will send participants a homework prompt prior to each group for exploring grief through art-making and creativity. The group will meet virtually to share and discuss their creative journey through grief. \nNo art experience needed. Participants can use their creative medium of choice (drawing\, writing\, photography\, nature collage\, sewing\, etc.). \nRegistration required. Call 919.719.7199. \nThursdays\,  1:00–3:00pm\nFebruary 5\nMarch 5\nApril 9\nMay 7 \n  \nTransitions GriefCare provides grief support at no charge to the bereaved. If you’d like to help us continue this service\, please consider making a donation at transitionslifecare.org/donate.
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/expressive-arts-virtual-5/2026-04-09/
LOCATION:Virtual
CATEGORIES:Grief Support,Grief Support for Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Journaling-scaled.jpg
GEO:35.7595731;-79.0192997
END:VEVENT
