SUMMARY:Grief Walk
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we seek comfort in nature and connection with others as we walk the paths at the Museum Park at the North Carolina Museum of Art. \nNote: The Park paths are paved with slight inclines. Please leave pets at home. You are welcome to attend some or all of the walking sessions. \nRegistration required. Call 919-719-7199. \nAll dates: Tuesdays\, 10:00–11:30am \nFebruary 10 and 24\nMarch 10 and 24\nApril 14 and 28\nMay 12 and 26
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/grief-walk-23/2026-04-14/
LOCATION:North Carolina Museum of Art\, 2110 Blue Ridge Rd\, Raleigh\, 27607\, United States
CATEGORIES:Grief Support,Grief Support for Adults
