SUMMARY:A Moment for Mindfulness (virtual)
DESCRIPTION:Mindfulness has been shown to help calm the grieving brain. Through gentle guidance\, we’ll explore mindfulness practices that help recognize the reality of loss and foster a sense of connection and peace. \nRegistration is required. Call 919-719-7199. \nWednesdays\, 12:00–1:00pm\nFebruary 18\nMarch 18\nApril 15\nMay 20 \nTransitions GriefCare provides grief support at no charge to the bereaved. If you’d like to help us continue this service\, please consider making a donation at transitionslifecare.org/donate.
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/a-moment-for-mindfulness-virtual-5/2026-04-15/
LOCATION:Virtual
CATEGORIES:Grief Support,Grief Support for Adults
